snippet.textDisplay:
Anthony, there is so much I wish I could say to you, but 1) you probably won't see this, 2) being vulnerable in this comment section isn't taking a chance on one person. 3) That said, just in case you see this comment...when the little came out , I hoped you would offer her a hug. This, however, was quickly joined by comments about not hugging her was respectable and respectful, etc. The whole Me Too movement and the profound effect it has had on men and their fear to offer a hug when someone is vulnerable and hurting, on interactions between the sexes/genders...

Thank you for the vulnerability YOU showed in this video, especially in that human moment. I am a touch starved person, single for past 12 years. I am trying to break out of that now and am finally ready to consider dating. Alone. I understand alone.

This is the first video of this man I have ever seen. Amazing.
